ygData.messageBody:
You don't say what your puter specs are..... if you have a lower end puter you should be ok with just old norrath EQ, you get the main continents but not velious and kunark.  If you only have windows 95 you are screwed.... can't run DX 8.1 on 95 or lower.  Check out the official site for info on tweaks for your particular configuration.  http://everquest.station.sony.com/eqlive/index.jsp
 
Have fun
Bebinn Maolcataig
37 Woodelf Ranger, Council of Truth
Bristlebane Server
